reviewText: Admittedly these videos hark back to an earlier age, however I hardly found them engaging or remotely clever. The make-up for the slime was fairly interesting, but that was about it. I'm sorry, but I couldn't detect much talent on display here.

A great collection of movies and short films from the twisted mind of Gregory Lamberson! Cult Classic Grindhouse fare with blood, guts and tons of action! Excellent! Highly Recommended! P.S. Run out and buy Slime City Massacre as well!
